paragraphs.title: Select Host
paragraphs.text:
val nodes = sqlContext.sql("select distinct node from nodes").collect().map(x => (x(0).asInstanceOf[String], x(0).asInstanceOf[String]))
val node = z.select("node", nodes)
val nodeApps = sqlContext.sql("select distinct service from services where service != 'consul' and node = '"+node+"'")
  .collect().map(x => (x(0).asInstanceOf[String], x(0).asInstanceOf[String]))
val app = z.select("app", nodeApps)
val appTable = app.asInstanceOf[String].replace("-", "_")+"_logs_enriched"

var query = """
select
 concat_ws(',', collect_list(time)) as time,
 concat_ws(',', collect_list(disk)) as Disk,
 concat_ws(',', collect_list(cpuuser)) as CPUUser,
 concat_ws(',', collect_list(cpusys as string)) as CPUSys,
 concat_ws(',', collect_list(cpu)) as CPU,
 concat_ws(',', collect_list(cast(round(100*memavailable/memtotal, 2) as string))) as Mem,
 concat_ws(',', collect_list(cast(greatest(app.requests, 0) as string))) as AppEvents,
 concat_ws(',', collect_list(cast(round(memavailable/1000, 0) as string))) as MemAvail
from (
  select
    date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') as time,
    cast(diskbusy as string) as Disk,
    cast(cpuuser as string) as CPUUser,
    cast(cpusys as string) as CPUSys,
    cast(round(100*memavailable/memtotal, 2) as string) as Mem,
    cast(greatest(app.requests, 0) as string) as AppEvents,
    cast(round(memavailable/1000, 0) as string) as MemAvail
  from node_monitoring
  left outer join (
    select date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') as time, node, count(*) as requests
    from """+appTable+"""
    group by date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm'), node
  ) app
  on node_monitoring.node = app.node and date_format(node_monitoring.datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') = app.time
  where node_monitoring.node = '"""+node+"""'
) a
group by node_monitoring.node
"""
println(query)
val data2 = sqlContext.sql(query)
z.angularBind("data2", data2.collect())
z.angularBind("data2Schema", data2.schema)
z.run("20160706-130128_836809999")

paragraphs.title: Host/Device View
Load Metrics
paragraphs.text:
val apps = sqlContext.sql("select distinct service from services where service != 'consul'").collect().map(x => (x(0).asInstanceOf[String], x(0).asInstanceOf[String]))
val app = z.select("app", apps)
val appTable = app.asInstanceOf[String].replace("-", "_")+"_logs_enriched"
val query = """
select
  concat(date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm'), ':00') as time,
  round(avg(cpuuser + cpusys)) as CPUUsed,
  round(avg(diskbusy)) as DISKUsed,
  round(avg(memavailable/memtotal)*100) as RAMUsed,
  round(avg(memavailable)/1000) as MemAvailable,
  sum(known.requests) as InternalRequests,
  sum(unknown.requests) as ExternalRequests,
  sum((known.requests + unknown.requests)) as TotalRequests
from node_monitoring
join (
  select
    date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') as time,
    1 as requests
  from """+appTable+"""
  where source_ip is not null or source_ip = '127.0.0.1'
) known on date_format(node_monitoring.datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') = known.time
join (
  select 
    date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') as time,
    1 as requests
  from """+appTable+"""
  where source_ip is null  
) unknown on date_format(node_monitoring.datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') = unknown.time
where node_monitoring.node in (
  select nodes.node from nodes
  join services on nodes.node = services.node
  where service = '"""+app+"""' 
)
group by date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm')
order by time asc
"""
val data1 = sqlContext.sql(query)
println(data1.count)
z.angularBind("data1", data1.collect())
z.angularBind("data1Schema", data1.schema)
z.run("20160807-021500_806175985")

select node, split(command, ' ')[0], avg(cpu) as avg
from ps_raw
group by node, split(command, ' ')[0]
order by avg desc
) a
where avg > 0

  concat(date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm'), ':00') as time,
  round(avg(cpuuser + cpusys)) as CPUUsed,
  round(avg(diskbusy)) as DISKUsed,
  round(avg(memavailable/memtotal)*100) as RAMUsed,
  round(avg(memavailable)/1000) as MemAvailable
  sum(known.requests) as InternalRequests,
  sum(unknown.requests) as ExternalRequests,
  sum((known.requests + unknown.requests)) as TotalRequests
from node_monitoring
join (
  select
    date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') as time,
    1 as requests
  from web_service_logs_enriched
  where source_ip is not null or source_ip = '127.0.0.1'
) known on date_format(node_monitoring.datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') = known.time
join (
  select 
    date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') as time,
    1 as requests
  from web_service_logs_enriched
  where source_ip is null  
) unknown on date_format(node_monitoring.datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') = unknown.time
where node_monitoring.node in (
  select nodes.node from nodes
  join services on nodes.node = services.node
  where service = 'web_service' 
)
group by date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm')
order by time asc
